<!-- Section 1: Heart for Strays -->
<h1 class="text-center mb-4">Heart for Strays</h1>

<div class="text-center">
    <p class="lead">
        Alongside my sister, I actively support stray and injured animals in our community through self-funded efforts.
        We provide food, basic medical care, and temporary shelter, and work to find permanent homes for rescued animals.
        Though not part of a formal organization, our work is driven by compassion and a commitment to animal welfare.
    </p>
</div>

