<!-- Section 3: Handmade Computer Models -->
<h1 class="text-center mb-4">Handmade Computer Models – School Department Showcase (Year 11)</h1>

<div class="text-center">
    <p class="lead">
        I created detailed handmade models of computer components using craft materials such as cardboard, paper, wires, and paint.
        These included models of a CPU, motherboard, keyboard, and internal hardware elements. The models were used to visually explain computer architecture to younger students and visitors.
        This project helped me combine creativity with technical knowledge, and it was appreciated for its accuracy and presentation.
    </p>
</div>

